
# PM2

Advanced, production process manager for node.js

npm install pm2 -g

## Features

A complete feature set for production environment, built with a
worldwide community of developers and entreprises.

pm2 start app.js

Behavior configuration      Cluster Mode
Source map support          Hot reload
Container integration       Development workflow
Watch & Reload              Startup Scripts
Log management              Deployment workflow
Monitoring                  PaaS Compatible
Module system               Keymetrics Monitoring
Max memory Reload           API


## Microservice

List all processes:
pm2 list

Act on them:

pm2 stop
pm2 restart
pm2 delete
